flowchart LR
  UI[Viewport] --> Scheduler[Tile Scheduler]
  Scheduler --> Cache{Tile Cache}
  Cache -- hit --> Compose[Compositor]
  Cache -- miss --> Backend[RenderBackend]
  Backend --> Pdfium[PDFium Adapter]
  Backend --> GPU[GPU Compositor Optional]
  Pdfium --> Bitmap[Rendered Tile]
  Bitmap --> Cache
  Compose --> TextLayer[Text Layer]
  Compose --> AnnotationLayer[Annotation Overlay]
  Compose --> RedactionLayer[Redaction Preview]
  Compose --> Screen[Display]
